hkgmoji\" />  定係返學校繼續練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我6點半開考</blockquote><br />\n反去練多一兩題 要keep狀態<br />\n但上年考生真情講一句 隊友係咩人最重要<br />\n利申上年隊友唔講野<br />\n一個人講左8分幾鐘<br />\n中途問佢地意見又唔講 唯有繼續獨腳戲<br />\n結果出黎4左"},{"pid":"ea2330c8197f6d96f82e06ac58b9aa2537d0916f","tid":153973,"uid":64492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T03:30:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問一個問題<br />\n<br />\n應該考之前訓一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  定係返學校繼續練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我6點半開考</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n輕鬆一下，但係唔好訓。一起身個人會好迷糊，諗唔到野。"},{"pid":"b5732c68720e5449a13cf62b0ec3f6913095db28","tid":153973,"uid":25029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T03:34:47.000Z","msg":"舊年我比人插咀打斷2次 3號同學又搶住黎講 全場講左2次 我考到一半面都紅哂想起身走 但最後都沉住氣 最後lv5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d53158aa82b619581e7606918dc05c5c432f65f","tid":153973,"uid":45603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T03:35:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唸住放棄算 下年再戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你D心態唔要得 捱埋佢呀巴打！"},{"pid":"24f563a9dd26a7bdd256efdb98b78bbd417d9466","tid":153973,"uid":24381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T03:37:47.000Z","msg":"考前一兩個鐘唔好練喇，你朝早練下，開下口講嘢，拎返個感覺啦，oral你練完作用唔大，隊友題目所有嘢都咁不穩，不如放鬆下自己啦。<br />\n利申：上年5*，今年再戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1851d5ad7c312eb618428f91ef4bd7f6992c9704","tid":153973,"uid":73222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T06:11:40.000Z","msg":"比心機呀巴打 一齊頂埋佢！<br />\n利申: 17 dse<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}